import React from 'react'

const CreatePost = () => {
    return (
        <form>
        <label>Title</label>
            <input type="text" name="title" onChange={this.onChange} value={this.state.title}/>
        <label>Content</label>
            <textarea name="content" onChange={this.onChange} value={this.state.content}></textarea>
        <button onClick={this.handleSubmit}>
            Submit
        </button>
    </form>
    )
}

export default CreatePost
